tr>\r\n<td>?</td>\r\n<td>Why were St Basil’s Management unable to contain the virus from spreading throughout the nursing home?</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>?</td>\r\n<td>What training was provided to staff on infection control and correct use of PPE? Please specify dates and type of training conducted</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>DUPLICATE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nWhat training was provided to staff on infection control and correct use of PPE? Please specify dates and type of training conducted</td>\r\n<td>ACP/ ACQSC</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>What infection control plan was executed at St Basil’s once the first COVID positive case was found?</td>\r\n<td>ACP/ACQSC</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>Why were St Basil’s Management unable to contain the virus from spreading throughout the nursing home?</td>\r\n<td> ACP/ACQSC\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>What training was provided to staff on infection control and correct use of PPE? Please specify dates and type of training conducted</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>Duplicate Question:\r\n\r\nWhat training was provided to staff on infection control and correct use of PPE? Please specify dates and type of training conducted</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>SPECIFIC CASE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nWhat was the exact date Tony Papantoniou’s mother was isolated in her room?</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>SPECIFIC CASE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nWhat were the exact dates Tony Papantoniou’s mother was tested for COVID-19? Provide copy of results.</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>SPECIFIC CASE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nIf Tony Papantoniou’s mother was isolated in her room how and why was she infected, when she is immobile and cannot leave her room without assistance?</td>\r\n<td>ACP</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>Why were families not informed when  the virus spread from high care nursing to other sections?</td>\r\n<td>ACP/ Independent evaluator</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>Please document the step-by-step process that took place when Aspen Medical took over. Families want to know why medical, dietary and care needs were not met</td>\r\n<td>DoH</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>SPECIFIC CASE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nWhy was Tony Papantoniou’s mother’s catheter care neglected and needed to be sent to hospital with a serious infection. Three weeks later it is still infected\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>ACP /ACQSC</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>SPECIFIC CASE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nWhy was Tony Papantoniou’s mother’s dehydrated and malnourished when admitted to      hospital on the 24th July?</td>\r\n<td>ACP /</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Tony Papantoniou</td>\r\n<td>SPECIFIC CASE QUESTION:\r\n\r\nTony Papantoniou is requesting a copy of his mother’s medical and dietary chart from the 01st July to the 24th of July. He needs a date this can be furnished</td>\r\n<td> ACP /ACQSC\r\n\r\n&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>Mon 24th</td>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Ton